title.rendered: 121 Why Belonging to an Exclusive Club could help your Amazon Business

content.rendered:
Podcast: Play in new window | Download (Duration: 4:29 — 4.1MB)

Subscribe: Spotify | Email | RSS

Detailed Research shows the truth: Your income is the average of the 10 people you spend the most time with.

So it follows that spending time with other successful people is going to increase your success! That’s the value of belonging to the right club!

Going to an exclusive gentleman’s Pall Mall club today reminded me of that. Of course, the exclusive London club for Amazon business owners is the Amazing FBA London Mastermind.

If you’re interested, click the link and find out the details.

If you want to join, like all good clubs, it’s by application only. Just look for “APPLY HERE” links. If you already know you want to apply, click here.

Watch Why Belonging to an Exclusive Club could help your Amazon Business
